text: Edouard Grethen (17 June 1903 - 2 April 1981) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1903 births Category:1981 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Luxembourg City
